parts.text: Create an alt text description that is helpful for screen readers and people who are blind or have visual impairment. Never start alt text with "Image of..." or "Picture of...". Please clearly identify the primary subject or subjects of the image. Describe what the subject is doing, if applicable. Please add a short description of the wider environment. If there is text in the image please transcribe and include it. Please describe the emotional tone of the image, if applicable. Do not use single or double quotes in the alt text.
